title: The Sannikov Land
occurrences: Over 100 years the mystery of the land spotted by Sannikov in the Arctic ice has excited many travellers, but no one could reach it. May be it was a land ice or the land had been immersed into the Arctic Ocean? Even nowadays Sannikov Land Bank still exists on geographical maps worldwide. This film is about everlasting quest and brave people that tried to peek beyond the horizon.
Baron Schtoll in the flesh. He was going to find the Sannikov Land.
- I intend to get to the Sannikov Land any time soon.
- I'm sure that Sannikov Land really exists. I'm going to find it...
- If you want to risk your life I suggest that you should go to the Sannikov Land with me.
My only offer is to go to the Sannikov Land with me.
That's the mystery of the Sannikov Land.
...The earthquake must have disrupted heater of the Sannikov Land...
